NOTICE: This software integrates with third-party APIs (BitSight, HaveIBeenPwned,
SecurityScorecard). Usage of those services is subject to their respective terms
of service and licensing agreements. SENTINEL does not redistribute any data from
those services — it only acts as a consumer of their APIs.

SENTINEL was built with a deterministic, audit-grade architecture. Any forked or
modified distribution must preserve the hash lineage chain and audit log contracts
to maintain compliance integrity. Distributions that remove or suppress audit
logging should not represent themselves as "audit-compliant."
